DescPort: <<
Nothing special needed other than the admin/ patch from kdebase and a
couple of small include fixes.  SANE does not exist in fink (yet?) so the
KDE scanner software will not be built (libsane/kooka).

NOTE: KDE packages do *not* have an -shlibs because of KDE's use of  
libltdl!  The .la's *must* be used in conjunction with the dynamic
libraries, and they are unversioned filenames, so multiple -shlibs would
conflict.
<<
